61
00:03:32,420 --> 00:03:37,020
♪The memories howl as they flash by♪

62
00:03:37,740 --> 00:03:42,100
♪Breaking free from
heavy shackles held tight♪

63
00:03:42,700 --> 00:03:47,060
♪In the darkness a lone lamp glows♪

64
00:03:47,740 --> 00:03:52,100
♪Light and shadows
criss-cross in the night♪

65
00:03:52,140 --> 00:03:53,220
♪Can't get rid of it♪

66
00:03:53,220 --> 00:03:54,500
♪Everything drowns♪

67
00:03:54,620 --> 00:03:57,580
♪No escape can yet be found♪

68
00:03:57,900 --> 00:04:01,780
♪The outline of sin♪

69
00:04:02,940 --> 00:04:07,780
♪On the bargaining table
right and wrong confound♪

70
00:04:07,820 --> 00:04:12,060
♪See the raging fiery light♪

71
00:04:12,180 --> 00:04:13,180
♪It will finally break free
from its plight♪

72
00:04:13,180 --> 00:04:14,540
♪Flooding over everything in its wake♪

73
00:04:14,660 --> 00:04:17,620
♪The escape will be found♪

74
00:04:29,920 --> 00:04:30,560
Mr. Zhu Jr.!

75
00:04:32,920 --> 00:04:33,440
Mr. Zhu Jr.!

76
00:04:37,960 --> 00:04:38,680
Mr. Zhu Jr.!

77
00:04:39,360 --> 00:04:40,400
Time to get up!

78
00:04:43,680 --> 00:04:44,480
What happened

79
00:04:45,600 --> 00:04:46,640
with you two last night?

80
00:04:47,600 --> 00:04:50,200
But she went downstairs for breakfast.
Master Zhu is there, too.

81
00:04:58,960 --> 00:04:59,480
Mr. Zhu Jr.!

82
00:05:04,280 --> 00:05:04,840
Bao'er!

83
00:05:04,840 --> 00:05:05,280
Father.

84
00:05:05,280 --> 00:05:05,880
Sit here.

85
00:05:07,840 --> 00:05:11,120
I had our cook make this nourishing soup
specially for you.

86
00:05:11,440 --> 00:05:12,440
Have some.

87
00:05:12,720 --> 00:05:15,800
I hope you will soon give our family
a child.

88
00:05:17,360 --> 00:05:18,360
Thanks, Father.

89
00:05:21,440 --> 00:05:23,680
From the first moment I saw you,

90
00:05:24,680 --> 00:05:28,000
I had a familiar feeling of you.

91
00:05:28,640 --> 00:05:30,040
I didn't expect that, in the end,

92
00:05:30,040 --> 00:05:32,600
you would really become
my daughter-in-law.

93
00:05:34,520 --> 00:05:37,520
Perhaps this was destined to be.

94
00:05:41,520 --> 00:05:42,080
Father,

95
00:05:42,720 --> 00:05:43,880
have some more.

96
00:05:44,280 --> 00:05:46,320
You have to live a very long life.

97
00:05:47,880 --> 00:05:49,440
Me? Forget that!

98
00:05:50,480 --> 00:05:51,360
Mr. Zhu Jr.!

99
00:05:54,520 --> 00:05:56,000
Go upstairs and get dressed!

100
00:05:56,520 --> 00:05:58,440
Look at you!
Where is your sense of decency?

101
00:06:09,720 --> 00:06:10,480
I...

102
00:06:12,120 --> 00:06:13,960
I'll go upstairs to change.

103
00:06:17,200 --> 00:06:17,920
Qiang,

104
00:06:22,640 --> 00:06:24,880
does Master know
that Guanwen was drunk last night?

105
00:06:25,200 --> 00:06:27,360
Master was in the study all night.

106
00:06:27,720 --> 00:06:29,480
He probably doesn't know
that Mr. Zhu Jr. drank.

107
00:06:29,720 --> 00:06:30,640
The study...

108
00:06:36,500 --> 00:06:39,460
[Huamei Clothing Store]

109
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:15,280
Ten for two of these.

110
00:07:15,280 --> 00:07:16,840
Ten? How about this?

111
00:07:25,880 --> 00:07:27,440
Mr. Zhu Jr.!

112
00:07:28,680 --> 00:07:29,200
What?

113
00:07:29,200 --> 00:07:30,240
Mrs. Zhu is kidnapped!

114
00:07:30,240 --> 00:07:30,760
What?

115
00:07:31,200 --> 00:07:31,760
Who kidnapped her?

116
00:07:31,760 --> 00:07:32,640
Dou Lili!

117
00:07:32,800 --> 00:07:33,400
Where did they go?

118
00:07:33,400 --> 00:07:34,320
I have no idea.

119
00:07:34,320 --> 00:07:36,160
She was in a car,
and I couldn't catch them.

120
00:07:36,200 --> 00:07:37,160
Should I call the police first?

121
00:07:37,160 --> 00:07:37,840
Listen,

122
00:07:37,920 --> 00:07:39,760
you go get help,
and I'll go to the Dou manor.

123
00:07:39,960 --> 00:07:40,640
OK!

124
00:08:14,040 --> 00:08:16,440
Well, well, Lin Bao'er.

125
00:08:17,360 --> 00:08:20,240
I thought you were afraid of nothing
in the world.

126
00:08:21,720 --> 00:08:22,880
If

127
00:08:23,400 --> 00:08:24,680
I press this thing

128
00:08:25,640 --> 00:08:27,120
on your face...

129
00:08:32,080 --> 00:08:34,160
Will Zhu Guanwen still want you?

130
00:08:37,560 --> 00:08:38,440
Now you are scared?

131
00:08:40,680 --> 00:08:41,480
Too late.

132
00:08:51,520 --> 00:08:52,920
If it wasn't for you,

133
00:08:52,920 --> 00:08:55,640
I'd be Mrs. Zhu by now.

134
00:08:56,560 --> 00:08:58,360
If it wasn't for you,

135
00:08:58,720 --> 00:09:00,720
I'd still be the mayor's daughter.

136
00:09:01,160 --> 00:09:04,320
If it wasn't for you,
everything wouldn't have happened!

137
00:09:30,040 --> 00:09:31,360
Zhu Guanwen, save me!

138
00:09:33,480 --> 00:09:34,560
At this point,

139
00:09:34,560 --> 00:09:36,320
are you still thinking
about Zhu Guanwen?

140
00:09:37,480 --> 00:09:38,160
Alright then,

141
00:09:46,800 --> 00:09:48,160
I will send you both

142
00:09:49,080 --> 00:09:50,400
to hell!

143
00:10:05,380 --> 00:10:07,860
♪The end has now been reached♪

144
00:10:08,140 --> 00:10:10,780
♪Yet we face each other in silence♪

145
00:10:11,480 --> 00:10:14,100
♪Looking away from you♪

146
00:10:14,140 --> 00:10:18,180
♪Emotions like a flood
they spread and grew♪

147
00:10:18,340 --> 00:10:21,660
♪Who would like to be fooled♪

148
00:10:22,740 --> 00:10:26,720
♪Love, how could it be a lie♪

149
00:10:30,340 --> 00:10:33,300
♪In a moment♪

150
00:10:33,340 --> 00:10:36,200
♪Flitting images flashing♪

151
